# Blogging Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 📝 BLOG REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define content categories
   - [ ] Plan content structure
   - [ ] Identify user roles
   - [ ] List required features
   - [ ] Document content workflow

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Reading mode optimization

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Article listing/grid
   - [ ] Article detail view
   - [ ] Category/tag system
   - [ ] Search functionality
   - [ ] Author profiles
   - [ ] Comments system
   - [ ] Newsletter integration
   - [ ] Social sharing

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── blog/
│   │   ├── ArticleCard.tsx
│   │   ├── ArticleGrid.tsx
│   │   ├── ArticleDetail.tsx
│   │   └── TableOfContents.tsx
│   ├── author/
│   │   ├── AuthorCard.tsx
│   │   └── AuthorProfile.tsx
│   ├── comments/
│   │   ├── CommentForm.tsx
│   │   └── CommentList.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx
│       ├── Newsletter.tsx
│       └── ShareButtons.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── articles/
│   ├── categories/
│   ├── authors/
│   └── search/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Content Structure
1. **Article Format**
   - Title: 60-70 characters
   - Meta description: 150-160 characters
   - Featured image: 1200x630px
   - Body: Markdown/Rich text
   - Categories and tags

2. **Typography**
   - Body text: 18-21px
   - Line height: 1.6
   - Paragraph spacing: 1.5em
   - Headers: modular scale 1.2

3. **Layout Principles**
   - Content width: 680px-720px
   - Sidebar width: 300px-320px
   - Grid system: 12 columns
   - Reading progress indicator

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Content Loading**
   - Lazy loading images
   - Infinite scroll/pagination
   - Content preloading
   - Image optimization

2. **Search Performance**
   - Instant search results
   - Debounced queries
   - Cached results
   - Search suggestions

3. **Comments System**
   - Lazy loading threads
   - Pagination/infinite scroll
   - Real-time updates
   - Spam protection

## 📱 Reading Experience

1. **Reading Mode**
   - Dark/light theme toggle
   - Font size adjustment
   - Line height control
   - Custom reading width

2. **Content Navigation**
   - Table of contents
   - Progress indicator
   - Smooth scroll
   - Bookmark system

## 🔒 Content Management

1. **Author Tools**
   - Rich text editor
   - Image management
   - Draft system
   - Version control

2. **Moderation Tools**
   - Comment moderation
   - User management
   - Content approval
   - Spam filtering

## 📱 Mobile-First Considerations

1. **Reading Experience**
   - Font size adaptation
   - Touch-friendly navigation
   - Offline reading
   - Share sheet integration

2. **Content Adaptation**
   - Responsive images
   - Collapsible sections
   - Mobile-optimized layout
   - Quick actions

